description: Poincaré series (or Molien series) for mod 2 cohomology of Lyons group.
links: A. Adem, Recent developments in the cohomology of finite groups, Notices Amer. Math. Soc., 44 (1997), 806-812.
maple: t1 + t^7/((1-t^4)*(1-t^6)*(1-t^7)); where t1 = Poincaré series in A014671.
author: Alejandro Adem (adem(AT)math.wisc.edu)
